# Testes API

Plano: [`docs/api-plan.md`](../../docs/api-plan.md#testes-e-coverage)

- Cada módulo catalog: `*.service.spec.ts` + `*.e2e-spec.ts`
- Meta: **≥ 80%** lines em `catalog/**/*.service.ts`
- E2E: GET 200 lista, GET 200 slug, GET 404 slug inválido
- Domain game (futuro): **≥ 90%** + casos PHB (d10 guerreiro, etc.)
- `npm run test:cov` antes de PR
